Feature: Validate Regressor Name against Series Group Name during Series Knowledge Onboarding

  As a system administrator,
  I want to ensure the Regressor Name is not the same as the Series Group Name,
  So that data integrity is maintained during the onboarding process.

  Scenario: Reject onboarding when Regressor Name matches Series Group Name
    Given a Series Group Name "SalesData"
    And a Regressor Name "SalesData"
    When the onboarding request is submitted
    Then the system should respond with a 400 status code
    And the response should include an error message indicating "Regressor Name cannot be the same as Series Group Name."

  Scenario: Allow onboarding when Regressor Name differs from Series Group Name
    Given a Series Group Name "SalesData"
    And a Regressor Name "MarketTrends"
    When the onboarding request is submitted
    Then the system should respond with a 201 status code
    And the response should confirm successful onboarding.
